  +zpaq-2.05.ebuild:
  Version bump. The new version fixes a crash when unpacking an unnamed file
  without renaming.

*zpaq-2.04-r1 (05 Jan 2011)

  05 Jan 2011; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org>
